<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Further BIM improvements ===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The [[Image:BIM_Views.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Views|Views]] panel got an overhaul and now has a section for all 2D views. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/15836 Pull request #15836]
* The [[Image:BIM_Views.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Views|Views]] panel got an activate and deactivate functionality for objects in the spatial decomposition section. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21239 Pull request #15836] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21570 Pull request #21570]
* NativeIFC support for 2D objects was added to BIM, allowing to embed 2D objects (linework, texts, dimensions) inside IFC files, as well as opening such files from other BIM apps. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/16629 Pull request #16629]
* The [[Image:Arch_Schedule.svg|24px]] [[Arch_Schedule|Schedule]] dialog gained support for simple arrays (e.g. non-nested). This enables regular and link arrays (both either expanded or not expanded) to be processed for further calculations in the BIM Schedule report. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19219 Pull request #19219]
* The ''Continue'' option is now stored separately for each Draft and BIM command. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20748 Pull request #20748]
* When adding BIM views to a TechDraw page, they now adhere to the page's scale, so that they have a sensible size. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/issues/20935 Pull request #20935]
* The default zoom level for new BIM projects has been changed to be more adequate to the magnitudes used for architectural models. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20271 Pull request #20271]
* When creating a new [[Image:Arch_Floor.svg|24px]] [[Arch_Floor|Level]], selected objects in the tree view are now included in the level. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20180 Pull request #20180]
* [[Image:Arch_Space.svg|24px]] [[Arch_Space|Spaces]] can now be created from a single object (e.g. the interior faces of a wall based on a rectangle base). [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20158 Pull request #20158]
* FreeCAD standard groups can now be ignored when a model is exported to IFC. This is controlled by a preference and is the new default. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21583 Pull request #21583]
* An option to preload all IfcTypes during IFC file import/open process has been added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21450 Pull request #21450]
* The [[Image:Arch_SectionPlane.svg|24px]] [[Arch_SectionPlane|Section Plane]] command received numerous fixes and usability improvements. Most notably the issue whereby rotating the section plane flipped the cut direction was fixed, and the ability to toggle the CutView from the Task panel was added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23826 Pull request #23826]
* Double clicking on a BIM object that supports editing should open its task panel, instead of editing its label. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23805 Pull request #23805], [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23796 Pull Request #23796] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/24712 Pull Request #24712] 
* The [[Image:Arch_Remove.svg|24px]] [[Arch_Remove|Remove]] command can now remove windows and doors from walls. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21561 Pull request #21561]
* When creating a custom window, the window's frame depth and related properties are described unambiguously to the user. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21486 Pull Request #21486]
* When exporting models that contain a roof, that roof is no longer removed from the export. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21409 Pull Request #21409]
* Double-clicking a [[Image:Arch_Floor.svg|24px]] [[Arch_Floor|Level]] now activates it and its working plane by default. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21159 Pull Request #21159]
* The {{KEY|W}}, {{KEY|P}} shortcut was added to select the working plane. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21157 Pull Request #21157].
* Support for B-splines for structures, such as [[Image:BIM_Slab.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Slab|Slab]], was added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21134 Pull Request #21134]
* Upon [[Image:Arch_Wall.svg|24px]] [[Arch_Wall|Wall]] creation, the wall's {{PropertyData|Offset}} property can additionally be entered. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21042 Pull Request #21042]
* The 2D View creation commands are now grouped together for improved usability. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20941 Pull Request #20941]
</div>

