{| cellpadding=5
| [[File:CAM_toolbit_library_manager_relnotes_1.1.png|384px]]
| The [[CAM_ToolBitLibraryOpen|Toolbit Library Editor]] was replaced and supports copy and paste as well as drag and drop features.
[https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23856 Pull request #23856]
|}
