<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Further CAM improvements ===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The [[Image:CAM_Shape.svg|24px]] [[CAM_Shape|CAM Shape]] experimental tool was replaced by ''Path from Shape with Tool Controller'' which is a significantly improved version of that tool based on a macro. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21108 Pull request #21108]
* Adaptive roughing/overhang detection was implemented including intelligent 2.5D projection of the model and stock for all adaptive operations, one-click "adaptive roughing" of the entire model, "Z stock to leave" setting to complement the "finishing stepdown" setting and a checkbox to order cuts by depth or region. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18880 Pull request #18880]
* G84/G74 tapping operations were added experimentaly. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/8069 Pull request #8069] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/24148 Pull request #24148]
* Multi-pass support was added for profile operations. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17326 Pull request #17326]
* Support for Snapmaker, Masso and Ondsel SVG postprocessors was added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20154 Pull request #20154], [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18845 Pull request #18845] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21743 Pull request #21743]
* The [[Image:CAM_SimulatorGL.svg|24px]] [[CAM_SimulatorGL|New CAM Simulator]] was improved, including two additional buttons to reset the camera and decrease the speed. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21288 Pull request #21288], [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21222 Pull request #21222] and more
* The [[CAM_Array|Array]] operation is now considered deprecated as it's currently also implemented as a dressup. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20321 Pull request #20321]
* Support for multi-pass profile operations was implemented. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17326 Pull request #17326]
* The [[CAM_DressupLeadInOut|LeadInOut]] functionality was improved. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22669 Pull request #22669]
* UI elements were added to allow viewing and editing tool controller parameters from within the operation's task panel. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23180 Pull request #23180]
</div>

<span id="Draft_Workbench"></span>
== Pracovní plocha Draft ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* Objects with two arrows can now have different start and end arrows. The size of an object's start and end arrows can also be different. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/11941 Pull request #11941]
* The [[Image:Draft_Edit.svg|24px]] [[Draft_Edit|Draft Edit]] command can now also handle [[Draft_Label|Draft Labels]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/13445 Pull request #13445]
* Support for relative file paths has been added to [[Image:Draft_ShapeString.svg|24px]] [[Draft_ShapeString|ShapeStrings]] and [[Image:Draft_Hatch.svg|24px]] [[Draft_Hatch|hatches]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17819 Pull request #17819] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17819 Pull request #23294]
* The handling of Links in [[TechDraw_DraftView|TechDraw DraftViews]] was fixed. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18175 Pull request #18175] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19296 Pull request #19296]
* The extrude mode of the [[Image:Draft_Trimex.svg|24px]] [[Draft_Trimex|Draft Trimex]] command has been made ''link-aware''. It can now handle faces belonging to Links and objects in linked containers. And the point that defines the extrusion can be co-planar with the face. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18314 Pull request #18314] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18320 Pull request #18320]
* The [[Draft_Move|Move]], [[Draft_Rotate|Rotate]] and [[Draft_Scale|Scale]] commands have been made ''link-aware'' as well. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18795 Pull request #18795]
* If a [[Draft_Facebinder|Facebinder]] based on connected faces is extruded, an attempt is made to close its corners. The ''Sew'' property of the object must be set to true for this. Note that the code can fail for complex shapes. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18901 Pull request #18901]
* [[Image:Draft_PathArray.svg|24px]] [[Draft_PathArray|Path arrays]] have been enhanced with several new properties. It is now possible to reverse the array, specify a fixed spacing unit, and use spacing patterns. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19017 Pull request #19017]
* Objects in [[Draft_Layer|layers]] can now have overrrides. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19207 Pull request #19207]
* The [[Image:Draft_AddToLayer.svg|24px]] [[Draft_AddToLayer|Draft AddToLayer]] command, to quickly put objects in the correct layer, has been added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19427 Pull request #19427]
* The TechDraw code that [[Draft_Hatch|Draft Hatch]] relies on has been revised to also handle dashed lines in hatch patterns. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19458 Pull request #19458]
* The [[Draft_Downgrade|Draft Downgrade]] and [[Draft_Upgrade|Draft Upgrade]] commands have been updated. [[Draft_Workbench#Draft_ArrayTools|Arrays]] can be downgraded (''exploded''), and new objects are put in the same container ([[Std_Group|Group]], [[Std_Part|Part]]) as the original objects, and also receive the visual properties of the original objects. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19487 Pull request #19487] and  [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19685 Pull request #19685]
* The [[Image:Draft_Polygon.svg|24px]] [[Draft_Polygon|Draft Polygon]] command now shows a preview (''tracker'') of an actual polygon, instead of a circle. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21045 Pull request #21045]
* An ''Align to face'' checkbox has been added to the task panel of the [[Image:Draft_Hatch.svg|24px]] [[Draft_Hatch|Draft Hatch]] command. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21332 Pull request #21332]
* An in-command shortcut {{KEY|D}} to recenter the working plane during commands has been added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19728 Pull request #19728]
* To simplify user input for single axis arrays, a ''linear mode'' option has been added to the task panel of the [[Image:Draft_OrthoArray.svg|24px]] [[Draft_OrthoArray|Draft OrthoArray]] command. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21602 Pull request #21602]
* Status bar hints were added for [[Draft_Workbench#Drafting|Draft Creation tools]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23244 Pull request #23244]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Further Draft improvements ===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The [[Draft_Fillet|Draft Fillet]] command now works on selected edges, instead of the first edge of selected objects. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17945 Pull request #17945] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18150 Pull request #18150]
* The [[Draft_AutoGroup|Draft AutoGroup]] and the [[Draft_AddToGroup|Draft AddToGroup]] commands have been improved. The menus of both commands are sorted alphabetically. In the menu of the [[Draft_AutoGroup|Draft AutoGroup]] command layers are separated from groups, and the ''New layer'' option prompts for a name and activates the layer. The actions of both commands have been made undoable. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18172 Pull request #18172] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19312 Pull request #19312]
* The position of the ''Scale multiplier'' field in the UI was improved ([[Draft_SetStyle|Draft SetStyle]], [[Draft_AnnotationStyleEditor|Draft AnnotationStyleEditor]] and [[Draft_Preferences|Draft Preferences]]). [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18299 Pull request #18299]
* The [[Draft_Draft2Sketch|Draft Draft2Sketch]] command now also applies coincident constraints between edges from different source objects. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18805 Pull request #18805]
* The radius, and chamfer and delete modes of the [[Draft_Fillet|Draft Fillet]] command are stored. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19067 Pull request #19067]
* An edit option has been added for [[Draft_Clone|Draft Clones]]. After double-clicking them in the [[Tree_view|Tree view]] their scaling can be modified in a task panel. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19477 Pull request #19477]
* A planar face and an edge can now be selected for the [[Draft_SelectPlane|Draft SelectPlane]] command. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19728 Pull request #19728]
* For clarity the ''Filled'' checkbox in the task panel of for example [[Draft_Wire|Draft Wire]] has been relabeled to ''Make face''. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19738 Pull request #19738]
* The texts of newly created dimensions are now oriented automatically relative to the current working plane. A [[Fine-tuning#Draft_Workbench|fine-tuning]] parameter is available to disable this behavior. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20072 Pull request #20072]
* [[Draft_Snap_Near|Near snap]] no longer overrides other snaps. On-object snaps, such as [[Draft_Snap_Midpoint|Midpoint snap]] and [[Draft_Snap_Endpoint|Endpoint snap]], within ''snapRange'' of the cursor are now detected. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20118 Pull request #20118]
* In the [[Draft_Preferences#Texts_and_dimensions|Draft Preferences]] a dropdown to select the font name for texts, dimensions and labels has been introduced. Previously the name had to be entered manually. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20400 Pull request #20400]
* The ''Continue'' option is now stored separately for each Draft and BIM command. For the [[Draft_Dimension|Draft Dimension]] command the old ''Continue'' option has been re-labeled to ''Chained mode'' for clarity, and a new ''Continue'' option has been added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20748 Pull request #20748]
* The [[Draft_ShapeString|Draft ShapeString]] command has seen several improvements. The font file is no longer a preference, instead the last selected file is stored. For the initial value of the font file an attempt is made to get a suitable file from the OS. This is primarily to help users who are not aware of font file locations. The last entered text and height are also stored. A ''Global'' option has been added to task panel. By unchecking that checkbox, coordinates can  be specified in the [[Draft_SelectPlane|working plane]] coordinate system. Finally, TrueType Collection font files ({{FileName|.ttc}}) can now also be selected, but only the first font in such a file can be used. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21004 Pull request #21004], [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21054 Pull request #21054] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21124 Pull request #21124]
* The base object for a [[Draft_Wire|Draft Wire]], [[Draft_BSpline|Draft BSpline]] and [[Draft_BezCurve|Draft BezCurve]] has been changed to the [[Part_Feature|Part::FeaturePython]] object. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21636 Pull request #21636]
* [[Draft_Snap_Intersection|Intersection snap]] now also detects intersections between faces and edges. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23352 Pull request #23352]
* The ''Working plane orientation'' option has been removed from the [[Draft_Scale|Draft Scale]] command as it did not work properly. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23716 Pull request #23716]
</div>

